+## About this fork of reVC
+This fork focuses on making GTA Vice City easier to debug/mod on modern handheld and desktop setups.
+
+Fork-specific changes (currently GTA VC focused):
+
+* Debug menu can be opened with `Ctrl+M` or `Select+B` (gamepad).
+* Added an Options-page helper hint: `DEBUG MENU: Ctrl+M or Select+B`.
+* Added `build_deck.sh` for a Steam Deck oriented build flow (Conan 1.x with dependency preflight).
+
+If you are here for a controller-friendly debug build of GTA VC, this is the point of this fork.
+
 ## Intro
 
 In this repository you'll find the fully reversed source code for GTA III ([master](https://github.com/GTAmodding/re3/tree/master/) branch) and GTA VC ([miami](https://github.com/GTAmodding/re3/tree/miami/) branch).
